   <body>
      <p>Divvun 2.0 with support for <strong>South Sámi</strong> was released on Desember 8, 2010. Divvun 2.0 does also
      include support for MS Office 2011 (Mac). Support for Office 2010 (Windows) and InDesign CS4 and CS5 is under
      development, but isn't ready yet.</p>
      <warning>Before you install Divvun 2.0 you must uninstall older versions of Divvun. Here you find instructions for
      <a href="userdocs/leaflet/win-install.html">Windows</a> and <a href="userdocs/leaflet/mac-install.html">MacOS X</a></warning>
